User case: Search Threads
Actor: User
Pre_condition: at least one key word is provided
Trigger: user request search the DB with a list of keywords

Evert Flow:
1. user request search the DB with a list of keywords
2. CircleRound search the whole DB and retrieve the relevant threads and show to the user
3. user choose one thread to see details
4. CircleRound GET all the details of this thread and show
